loves this town better than I do.

25:54.303 --> 25:58.296
No, you love power, Jim. That's it.

25:58.932 --> 26:01.139
Now, we take down Max
and we are done.

26:01.310 --> 26:02.971
And then I'm gonna do whatever
I have to do

26:03.145 --> 26:05.887
to make sure that
I knock you off of your throne.

26:16.033 --> 26:19.025
- Norrie, where's Joe?
- I don't know.

