26:23.999 --> 26:25.910
He wouldn't try to come back
in this storm.

26:26.085 --> 26:28.667
- We barely made it ourselves.
- Yeah, that was SO weird.

26:28.837 --> 26:32.500
- It came out of nowhere.
- Yeah, maybe not.

26:34.510 --> 26:36.466
- You guys.
- Joe, where have you been?

26:36.637 --> 26:38.218
NORRIE: Where's Julia?
- She got Shot.

26:38.388 --> 26:40.299
ANGIE: What?
- Yeah, in the chest.

26:40.474 --> 26:43.466
And then She died for a minute,
but She's gonna be okay.

26:44.019 --> 26:47.261
Barbie brought her back.
It was incredible.

26:47.439 --> 26:50.397
- Thank God.
JOE: Guys.

26:51.693 --> 26:53.399
I think he might be the monarch.

26:54.363 --> 26:57.230
The tornado went away right after
he finished sucking the air

26:57.407 --> 26:58.908
- out of her chest, it was--
- Ew.

26:59.701 --> 27:03.444
- No, that's not why the storm stopped.
- What?

27:06.041 --> 27:07.906
It stopped because
I decided to come back.

27:09.294 --> 27:10.374
Okay.

27:10.879 --> 27:14.497
Look, something started it
and something stopped it.

27:15.843 --> 27:17.128
