27:19.346 --> 27:21.382
We need to go to the dome.

27:21.974 --> 27:23.384
Wh--?

27:25.561 --> 27:26.892
The big dome.

27:30.274 --> 27:33.687
Right. If these stars are really us,

27:33.861 --> 27:36.773
then we have to go to the same Spot
on the big dome.

27:37.823 --> 27:41.907
Under the North Star, due north.

27:42.077 --> 27:44.568
That's right around
the Bollingwood Bridge.

27:45.080 --> 27:46.866
And then what?

27:47.833 --> 27:51.872
I don't know. Stuff happened
when we touched it together.

27:52.296 --> 27:57.541
Okay, so the four of uS
need to do the exact same thing.

27:58.760 --> 28:02.753
Enough guessing.
The dome owes us some answers.

28:10.022 --> 28:11.228
So, what's the plan?

28:12.900 --> 28:14.856
March right in, let her ambush us?

28:15.027 --> 28:17.268
We're not going in the front door.

28:17.446 --> 28:19.653
Julia Showed me another way
the day the miSSile hit.

28:20.199 --> 28:22.656
