28:30.459 --> 28:31.494
BARBIE:
Just in case.

28:43.055 --> 28:44.420
Let's go.

28:55.067 --> 28:59.060
Julia'S car is gone.
I gueSS Barbie took her.

29:00.864 --> 29:02.365
Oh, God.

29:02.824 --> 29:04.655
I didn't think he could ever
go this far.

29:08.413 --> 29:12.747
- How well do you know Barbie?
- I don't think anybody knows him.

29:12.918 --> 29:15.785
Julia does. Or thought She did.

29:16.922 --> 29:18.708
Peter Shumway...

29:19.800 --> 29:24.965
He was in deep.
He bet the house. Literally.

29:25.889 --> 29:29.097
- The house.
- And lost.

29:29.268 --> 29:33.261
And Barbie was the collection agent.
Wasn't too polite about it either.

29:33.814 --> 29:36.977
- Do you really think--?
- If Barbie killed Peter...

29:39.861 --> 29:41.567
And then Julia found out.

29:56.461 --> 29:57.576
JIM:
I don't know about this.

29:57.754 --> 30:00.131
Would you just Shut your mouth
for once?

30:02.801 --> 30:04.541
Hello, boyS.

30:06.680 --> 30:08.170
Keep walking.

30:18.275 --> 30:21.483
MAN: That's all they were packing.
