thick sometimes.

30:48.430 --> 30:49.590
What do you mean?

30:50.140 --> 30:54.099
I mean, I'm giving you a chance
to live.

30:54.895 --> 30:59.229
What, with you?
Max, you Shot Julia.

30:59.399 --> 31:03.642
- She was never right for you anyway.
- You're the one who's not right, Max.

31:13.497 --> 31:15.362
I had plans for you.

31:19.086 --> 31:23.420
I trusted you
and you screwed me over.

31:26.218 --> 31:29.506
You're no different from him
or from anyone else in this town.

31:29.679 --> 31:32.637
- Look who's talking.
- No, that is not true, Jim!

31:32.808 --> 31:36.471
I am nothing like you!
I am a survivor.

31:38.814 --> 31:41.021
If you have plans to be somewhere,

31:41.608 --> 31:45.442
then someone iS going to be
