33:47.317 --> 33:49.057
I was next!

33:51.821 --> 33:55.439
Back up, Barbie.
Put the weapon down.

34:09.005 --> 34:11.041
Put your hands behind your back.

34:11.967 --> 34:14.925
- You killed your last victim.
- Spread your legS apart.

34:15.095 --> 34:16.631
