JIM: Am I set?
- Two secs. Almost there.

34:48.086 --> 34:50.042
- Hey, Jim?
- Yeah?

34:50.213 --> 34:53.171
I heard something today.
From the outside.

34:53.341 --> 34:54.717
It was about Barbie.

34:55.927 --> 34:57.087
What are you talking about?

34:57.887 --> 35:00.094
It was the military.
They know he's in here.

35:01.474 --> 35:03.556
Tell me exactly what they said.

35:05.020 --> 35:09.184
They said that he's the one.
The one that they've been looking for.

35:10.817 --> 35:11.852
Turn it on.

35:14.529 --> 35:16.360
ThiS iS Jim Rennie.

